snippet.title: Overlook Trail video game trailer
snippet.description:
Wislist on Steam: https://s.team/a/817800 

Embark on Overlook Trail, an upcoming video game from Longhand Electric

Overlook Trail is a mixtape of arcade gameplay, 3D platforming, and peculiar puzzles. Navigate through surreal landscapes with ever-changing challenges. Coming to Steam in early 2025.
